<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
iflag                       : displays the settings of your iflags<br>
iflag [flag name]           : turns a info sub-channel off<br>
iflag [flag name] [setting] : sets an iflag to a given level<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
Iflags are a method to control how much information about various happens<br>
on the mud is conveyed to you.  Iflags can range from level 0 to level 3<br>
where level 0 is off and level 3 is most verbose.<br>
<br>
See also: message, info, options<br>
</html>
</body>
